  stimulus_text = 'The story of the Wright brothers’ development of the first successful airplane is one of perseverance and innovation. The brothers experimented with numerous designs, faced countless setbacks, and refused to give up on their dream of flight.  Even though they didn’t have the benefit of modern technology, the Wright brothers’ determination and ingenuity enabled them to achieve their goal, which had eluded many before them. Which of the following best summarizes the main idea of the passage?',
