  stimulus_text = 'When the character says, "He is at war with his past," he is referring to the protagonist’s struggle to come to terms with his past actions. The character’s past actions have consequences that he is trying to work through, but he feels trapped by these consequences. The protagonist is trying to understand how his past actions have shaped his current life and how he can move forward.',
